   { helloworld:
      { name: 'helloworld',
        messages:
         { HelloRequest:
            { name: 'HelloRequest',
              fields:
               [ { name: 'name',
                   type: 'string',
                   id: 1,
                   required: false,
                   repeated: false,
                   map: false,
                   defaultValue: '' } ] },
           HelloReply:
            { name: 'HelloReply',
              fields:
               [ { name: 'message',
                   type: 'string',
                   id: 1,
                   required: false,
                   repeated: false,
                   map: false,
                   defaultValue: '' } ] } },
        services:
         { Greeter:
            { name: 'Greeter',
              methods:
               [ { name: 'SayHello',
                   requestStream: false,
                   responseStream: false,
                   requestName: 'HelloRequest',
                   responseName: 'HelloReply' } ] } } } },
  file: '/Users/me/protos/helloworld.proto',
  options:
   { java_multiple_files: true,
     java_package: 'io.grpc.examples.helloworld',
     java_outer_classname: 'HelloWorldProto',
     objc_class_prefix: 'HLW' } }
```

**NOTE** If no package name is specified in the protocol buffer definition an empty `''` string is used for the package / namespace name.

